q 0.5 G 1 w 72 730 m 540 730 l S Q
BT 0 g /F2 12 Tf 72 700 Td (Radical Acceptance means:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 675 Td (- Accepting reality AS IT IS \(not approving of it\)) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 655 Td (- Letting go of fighting against what already happened) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 635 Td (- Choosing to stop adding suffering to pain) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 12 Tf 72 600 Td (Pain + Non-Acceptance = SUFFERING) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 12 Tf 72 578 Td (Pain + Acceptance = PAIN \(just pain, which passes\)) Tj ET
