BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 515 Td (___________________________________________________________________) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 485 Td (Ways I am fighting reality: ________________________________________) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 72 460 Td (___________________________________________________________________) Tj ET
